narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Developing an original musical. Studying the historical context of the piece as well as learning about and engaging in the process of creating and mounting a new work and originating roles. The class was exciting, stimulating, challenging, and fun. Annette is incredible.
Absolutely, loved every second of it.
Definitely take a production seminar if you can. You get academic credit for doing theater!
